ticle/.premium/hamas-is-in-no-hurry-to-seal-a-hostage-deal-neither-is-netanyahus-government/0000018d-7b29-d008-a9cd-fbfd41600000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列士兵在黎巴嫩边境被反坦克导弹弹片轻伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article-live/netanyahu-gaza-war-will-take-months-not-years-un-to-investigate-unrwa/0000018d-7c7a-dcdb-a58d-fd7fcd7e0000</link><description>真主党称其使用伊朗制造的 Falaq-1 重型导弹瞄准以色列北部。 ■ 巴勒斯坦人向以色列北部基布兹开枪，房屋受损；以色列国防军搜寻枪手 ■ 也门胡塞武装称他们向红海两艘船发射导弹</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 03:43:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article-live/netanyahu-gaza-war-will-take-months-not-years-un-to-investigate-unrwa/0000018d-7c7a-dcdb-a58d-fd7fcd7e0000</guid></item><item><title>“对我来说是一个转折点”：加拿大主要自由主义犹太复国主义团体领导人辞职，称 10 月 7 日将他推向了右翼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/head-of-canadas-leading-liberal-zionist-group-quits-saying-oct-7-pushed-him-to-the-right/0000018d-7ba2-d008-a9cd-fbf793dd0000</link><description>乔·罗伯茨 (Joe Roberts) 发帖称，哈马斯的袭击动摇了他的政治信仰，以至于他不再认同 JSpace 的议程</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 00:03:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/head-of-canadas-leading-liberal-zionist-group-quits-saying-oct-7-pushed-him-to-the-right/0000018d-7ba2-d008-a9cd-fbf793dd0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡祝愿查尔斯国王在癌症诊断后“身体健康”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-wishes-king-charles-good-health-after-cancer-diagnosis/0000018d-7b31-dcdb-a58d-ff3da7a00001</link><description>白金汉宫周一宣布，75岁的英国君主将暂停公共活动，但将继续处理国家事务</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 21:47:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-wishes-king-charles-good-health-after-cancer-diagnosis/0000018d-7b31-dcdb-a58d-ff3da7a00001</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院调查史无前例的合理性标准判决泄露事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-to-investigate-unprecedented-leak-of-reasonableness-standard-decision/0000018d-7ad6-d008-a9cd-fbf7b2600000</link><description>以色列高等法院组成的小组将调查政府合理性立法中的决定是如何在宣布之前被泄露的</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 21:19:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-to-investigate-unprecedented-leak-of-reasonableness-standard-decision/0000018d-7ad6-d008-a9cd-fbf7b2600000</guid></item><item><title>以色列财长承诺积极反对美国对约旦河西岸定居者的制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-finance-minister-pledges-to-actively-oppose-american-sanctions-on-w-bank-settlers/0000018d-7aa0-dcdb-a58d-ffbdab380000</link><description>几位以色列议员严厉批评拜登对约旦河西岸暴力定居者的新制裁，以及开始执行这些制裁的两家以色列银行</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 20:20:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-finance-minister-pledges-to-actively-oppose-american-sanctions-on-w-bank-settlers/0000018d-7aa0-dcdb-a58d-ffbdab380000</guid></item><item><title>马尔万·巴尔古提 (Marwan Barghouti) 是谁？被监禁的恐怖分子还是巴勒斯坦曼德拉？为什么哈马斯希望释放他？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/who-is-marwan-barghouti-jailed-terrorist-or-palestinian-mandela/0000018d-794b-dd6e-a98d-fd6b6b8e0000</link><description>长期以来被视为巴勒斯坦权力机构主席马哈茂德·阿巴斯的继任者的马尔万·巴尔古提因谋杀罪在以色列服五次无期徒刑。哈马斯特别要求在可能的人质囚犯交换中释放他。巴尔古提是团结的实用主义者还是恐怖分子的策划者？</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 19:43:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/who-is-marwan-barghouti-jailed-terrorist-or-palestinian-mandela/0000018d-794b-dd6e-a98d-fd6b6b8e0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列极右翼反对释放哈马斯扣押的以色列人质的协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-05/ty-article/.highlight/why-israels-far-right-opposes-a-deal-to-free-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas/0000018d-7a76-d9fb-a9fd-feff97bb0000</link><description>尽管我们过去失败了，但我们有一个完整的假设未来来阻止我们被迫释放的任何邪恶。与鲁莽的部长本·格维尔（Ben-Gvir）强迫他的保安玩捉迷藏不同，人质已经没有时间了</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 18:40:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-05/ty-article/.highlight/why-israels-far-right-opposes-a-deal-to-free-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas/0000018d-7a76-d9fb-a9fd-feff97bb0000</guid></item><item><title>卫星图像显示以色列对真主党无人机基地的袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-strike-on-hezbollah-drone-base-revealed-in-satellite-images/0000018d-7a19-dcdb-a58d-ff1da1370000</link><description>十天前真主党向以色列铁穹电池发射攻击无人机后，黎巴嫩空军基地成为袭击目标。新的镜头显示了受损的跑道和附近的机库</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 17:46:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-strike-on-hezbollah-drone-base-revealed-in-satellite-images/0000018d-7a19-dcdb-a58d-ff1da1370000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法院批准对被指控妨碍谋杀调查的警察进行宽大的认罪交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-approves-plea-bargain-for-cop-charged-with-obstructing-murder-investigation/0000018d-79d4-d008-a9cd-fbf5c55a0000</link><description>首席准尉哈伊姆·加拜 (Chaim Gabai) 未能报告他与以色列北部谋杀案主要嫌疑人的关系，将被判犯有欺诈和背信罪，而对他的主要指控——妨碍司法公正——则被撤销</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 17:21:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-approves-plea-bargain-for-cop-charged-with-obstructing-murder-investigation/0000018d-79d4-d008-a9cd-fbf5c55a0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔部长逃离约旦河西岸的安全时，保镖被迫追赶他</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/bodyguards-forced-to-chase-minister-ben-gvir-as-he-flees-his-own-security-in-the-west-bank/0000018d-79c6-d9fb-a9fd-ffdfca510000</link><description>拥有最严格安全级别的以色列国家安全部长对他的安全团队感到愤怒，并在警卫还没准备好后就上了邻居的车</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 17:07:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/bodyguards-forced-to-chase-minister-ben-gvir-as-he-flees-his-own-security-in-the-west-bank/0000018d-79c6-d9fb-a9fd-ffdfca510000</guid></item><item><title>由于需求低迷，以色列航空公司取消了夏季飞往​​都柏林和马拉喀什的航班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/el-al-cancels-summer-flights-to-dublin-and-marrakech-due-to-low-demand/0000018d-79d7-d008-a9cd-fbf75bd30000</link><description>以色列航空公司坚称取消两条线路的决定完全是基于客户的需求，而不是基于爱尔兰和摩洛哥对以色列加沙战争的政治立场</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 16:11:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/el-al-cancels-summer-flights-to-dublin-and-marrakech-due-to-low-demand/0000018d-79d7-d008-a9cd-fbf75bd30000</guid></item><item><title>第二家以色列银行根据美国制裁封锁西岸定居者的账户</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/second-israeli-bank-blocks-west-bank-settlers-account-in-compliance-with-u-s-sanctions/0000018d-795e-de30-a5dd-79ffa4990000</link><description>以色列政府拥有的邮政银行关闭了被列入美国制裁名单的戴维·柴·哈斯代 (David Chai Hasdai) 的账户，而一天前以色列银行也采取了类似行动；以色列央行发表声明支持雷米遵守制裁的决定</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 16:02:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/second-israeli-bank-blocks-west-bank-settlers-account-in-compliance-with-u-s-sanctions/0000018d-795e-de30-a5dd-79ffa4990000</guid></item><item><title>新星党大屠杀受害者家属要求以色列立法者给出答案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/families-of-nova-party-massacre-victims-demand-answers-from-israeli-lawmakers/0000018d-7986-d008-a9cd-fbf7fbf50000</link><description>家人在议会听证会上表示，他们没有收到有关亲人遭遇的信息，国家也没有向他们提供支持</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 15:44:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/families-of-nova-party-massacre-