haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-lawyer-to-qatari-state-fund-advises-idf-in-hostage-negotiations/0000018d-7929-d4f1-a18d-fd7954b70000</link><description>律师约瑟夫·本克尔代表卡塔尔慈善机构，这是卡塔尔政府控制的一个基金会，曾被用来向哈马斯转移资金。战争爆发后，本克尔被征召入以色列陆军预备役，担任人质谈判顾问</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 13:20:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-lawyer-to-qatari-state-fund-advises-idf-in-hostage-negotiations/0000018d-7929-d4f1-a18d-fd7954b70000</guid></item></channel></rss>